> @sipsorcery Any idea why this doesn't compile on msvc?

@MarcoFalke I'll be able to have a closer look later. 

From a quick glance my first guess would be that if there's a clock involved gcc and msvc do things differently, see this [SO question]( https://stackoverflow.com/questions/43276695/stdchronosystem-clock-vs-stdchronohigh-resolution-clock-behavior/43279646).

